[PROMPT]  [TARGETLANGUAGE] I want you to act like a SEO Keywords Explorer. I will give you the company product or services and you will give the top 10 keywords category based on the following:
1. Seed keywords
2. Keywords by search intent
3. Long-tail keywords (topical and supporting)
4. Low-competition keywords
5. Niche keywords
6. Branded and unbranded keywords
7. Your competitors' keywords
8. Primary and secondary keywords
I dont need explanations. Do you understand? [TARGETLANGUAGE][PROMPT]
title: Mastermind Keyword Explorer
